{"type":"article","id":23373,"title":"美國威斯康辛州基諾沙巿一名黑人遭到警察槍擊","uid":1654,"topics":[254,9697,312,10582],"contents":"<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/us/police-involved-shooting-in-wisconsin-prompts-violent-protest-report\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結<br>\n<br>\n</a>［簡報］<br>\n據報當地時間星期日，<br>\n一名黑人Jacob Blake遭到警察從背後射擊，<br>\n該人身中數發子彈，現送院搶救中，情況嚴重。<br>\n目前司法部門正在調整事件。<br>\n<br>\n［個人意見］<br>\n由於本案目前有不明朗因素，<br>\n故鄙人尚未能就「案件本身」作任何評論，<br>\n無論被害人<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MrAndyNgo/status/1297776854670008320\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">背景如何</a>，<br>\n畢竟連執勤記錄都未公布，<br>\n誰知道會否又跟<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XkoGZIYvWm0\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">2014年</a>和<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NjKjaCvXdf4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">今年5月</a>那兩宗案一樣翻車呢？<br>\n<br>\n不得不說的是，<br>\n今次主流媒體的反應真是快，<br>\n離此案發生不足二十四小時<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/23/us/kenosha-police-shooting.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">便有</a>跟進<a href=\"https://abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory/protest-erupts-wisconsin-police-shoot-man-72563698\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">報導</a>了；<br>\n和之前的黑人射殺小孩案相比，<br>\n真是天差地別。<br>\n<br>\n另一群反應迅速的團隊則非「安提法燒掠殺聯盟」莫屬，<br>\n案發不久便於該地<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MrAndyNgo/status/1297755215576174593\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">築營火</a>、<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MrAndyNgo/status/1297777382439317505\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">買免錢</a>，以及<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MrAndyNgo/status/1297770791891656706\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">行使持槍權</a>了。","date":"2020-08-24","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}